---
title: Beyond Meat® Ragù with Orzo and Cheesy Toasts
description: In this meal, Beyond Meat®, spinach and crushed tomatoes are the building blocks of a delicious sauce that gets paired with buttery orzo pasta. We can't forget a side of cheesy garlic bread for scooping up every morsel!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-au-beyond-meat-b80de63c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/beyond-meat-ragu-652e3fb91ead9e91b2044a87-36ceb610.pdf
